lead_paragraph: Brian Dozier broke out of a slump with three hits and the Minnesota Twins snapped Dallas Keuchel's 17-game home winning streak with a 6-2 victory over the Houston Astros on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Twins End Keuchel's 17-Game Home Win Streak, Beat Astros 6-2
